cause_of_action: tort of abuse of process claim
relevant_rule: Rule 221 of the Federal Courts Rules
application_details: TSC alleged Tractor Supply initiated litigation to devalue TSC's business during a takeover bid
decision_reasoning: not plain and obvious that TSC could not succeed
does not meet the two-part test for abuse of process (improper purpose + overt act)
procedure_steps: Prothonotary Milczynski initially dismissed the motion to strike
Tractor Supply appealed, arguing lack of jurisdiction and failure to meet the abuse of process test
